{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"原因\"><a href=\"#%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>原因</h1>\n<p>硬件加速背后的原理，请参考：<a href=\"https://www.sitepoint.com/introduction-to-hardware-acceleration-css-animations/\">https://www.sitepoint.com/introduction-to-hardware-acceleration-css-animations/</a></p>\n<h1 id=\"使用方法\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>使用方法</h1>\n<p>并不是所有的CSS元素属性都可以开启硬件加速，只有下面几个可以开启硬件加速： </p>\n<ul>\n<li>transform  </li>\n<li>opacity  </li>\n<li>filter  </li>\n</ul>\n<p>只要在元素添加这三个属性之一就可以开启。注意：CSS3的兼容性。你需要自行添加前缀。</p>\n<h1 id=\"参考链接\"><a href=\"#%E5%8F%82%E8%80%83%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>参考链接</h1>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.sitepoint.com/introduction-to-hardware-acceleration-css-animations/\">https://www.sitepoint.com/introduction-to-hardware-acceleration-css-animations/</a></li>\n</ol>","timeToRead":1,"excerpt":"原因 硬件加速背后的原理，请参考： https://www.sitepoint.com/introduction-to-hardware-acceleration-css-animations/ 使用方法 并不是所有的CSS…","frontmatter":{"title":"css硬件加速","cover":null,"date":"2017-02-04T10:08:29.000Z","category":"css优化","tags":["css硬件加速"]},"fields":{"nextTitle":"css设计模式","nextSlug":"/css/css-design-pattern/","prevTitle":"number 常用方法","prevSlug":"/javascript/number/number/","slug":"/css/css-hardware-accelerated/","date":"2017-02-03T16:00:00.000Z"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/css/css-hardware-accelerated/"}}